descript.abstract: Location of fishing access points in Kentucky. A SQL database of fishing access sites is maintained by KDFWR fisheries, and is used to drive this feature class as well as the "Where to fish" web site https://app.fw.ky.gov/fisheries/waterbody.aspx . All sites in here should be public accessible, and the feature class includes a name and waterbody associated with the access.
descript.purpose: Used to delineate point location for fishing ramps (any boat, small boat only, or Carrydown only), docks, piers, and bank access.
descript.supplinf:
This information is also available on the Fishing and Boating Access web site http://fw.ky.gov/app1/waterbody.aspx, as well as the interactive hunting and fishing web site. http://kygeonet.ky.gov/kdfwr/viewer.htm
A paper version of this data from Spring 2009 Kentucky's Boating and Fishing access sites is available by calling 1-800-858-1549

dataIdInfo.idAbs: Location of fishing access points in Kentucky. A SQL database of fishing access sites is maintained by KDFWR fisheries, and is used to drive this feature class as well as the "Where to fish" web site https://app.fw.ky.gov/fisheries/waterbody.aspx . All sites in here should be public accessible, and the feature class includes a name and waterbody associated with the access.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: Used to delineate point location for fishing ramps (any boat, small boat only, or Carrydown only), docks, piers, and bank access.
